Richard Massingham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Massingham 0 Richard Massingham (31 January 1898 in Sleaford, Lincolnshire – 1 April 1953 in Biddenden, Kent) was a British actor who is principally noted for starring in public information films made in the 1940s and early 1950s.
